# Invariants (repository hygiene — not storefront runtime):
# - Never commit Shopify CLI auth/state, API tokens, .env material, or private keys/SSH identities (supply-chain + account takeover).
# - add-to-cart concurrency, fetch timeouts, Liquid null-safety, CLS: enforced in theme source, not here.
# - Do not add broad ignores (e.g. /assets, /config) that would drop theme files from version control.

# OS
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
ehthumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# Editors / IDEs
.idea/
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
!.vscode/settings.json
*.swp
*.swo
*~
*.orig

# Shopify CLI / local tooling
.shopify/
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Secrets & keys (accidental paste into repo root)
*.pem
*.crt
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
id_rsa
id_ed25519
id_ecdsa

# Logs and caches
*.log
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnpm-debug.log*

# Node / test tooling
node_modules/
dist/
build/
coverage/
.nyc_output/

# Archives / accidental exports
*.zip
*.tar
*.tar.gz
